			<h2>Privacy</h2><br />
			
<p>To better protect your privacy and personal information we provide this statement explaining our online information policy.</p><br />

<p>We use the information you provide about yourself when making an enquiry only to help you find a room. We do not share this information with outside parties except to the extent necessary to complete your requirements in seeking accommodation in Japan.</p><br />

<p>We use return email addresses to answer the email we receive. These are not used for any other purpose and are not shared with other companies or organisations. You can register with our website if you would like to receive our newsletter as well as updates on our new properties and services. Information you submit on our website will not be used for this purpose unless you opt in for it.</p><br />

<p>We never use or share the personally identifiable information provided to us online in ways unrelated to the ones described above without also providing you an opportunity to opt-out or otherwise prohibit such unrelated uses.</p><br />

